    "body": "How would the Players tab look like in your mock up?  The tabs on top conflict with the column labels.\n\nMusic controls in the lobby was a long-requested feature.  Setting up a MP game can take quite a while (waiting for players, choosing options, general chatting), and previously players would need to leave the lobby (and possibly lose their spot) if they want to change the music track.\n"
